Aceso Recovery

{/* Albumtitle */}

The Problem

Athletes aren't returning to sport post op.

Surgeon's take the blame for poor outcomes.

When sport related injuries (like an ACL tear) require surgery, the surgeon's process is basically perfected.

So why do you hear so often that athletes can't return to sport after recovery?

Aceso is a dual sided SaaS company ran by myself (CTO) and my co-founder Josh Woods (CEO). We believe the tech world has left the world of physical therapy in the dust, leaving both patients and therapists at a disadvantage.

) }
